The use of GPUs and large datasets suggests that the paper is likely to be in the cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-category. Additionally, the mention of optimization algorithms and convergence issues suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of distributed computing suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) sub-category.
